&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="http://blog.mintek.com/Enterprise_Asset_Management/bid/38027/Battling-The-Skilled-Maintenance-Worker-Crisis-With-An-EAM" title="Battling The Skilled Maintenance Worker Crisis With An EAM"&gt;Battling The Skilled Maintenance Worker Crisis With An EAM&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
